## INIT State Immediate Actions

### THE MOMENT YOU ENTER THIS STATE:

```bash
# üî¥üî¥üî¥ STEP 0: CHECK FOR COMPACTION (HIGHEST PRIORITY) üî¥üî¥üî¥
